+   code --version
+   ```
+
+3. **cgc CLI** installed
+   ```bash
+   pip install codegraphcontext
+   cgc --version
+   ```
+
+4. **A test project** to index (optional but recommended)
+
+## 🚀 Installation Steps
+
+### Step 1: Navigate to Extension Directory
+```bash
+cd /home/shashank/Desktop/CodeGraphContext/vscode-extension
+```
+
